THis repository was created using :.
http://blog.stuartherbert.com/php/2011/09/22/php-components-publishing-your-pear-channel-on-github/


How to tweak a package.xml painlessly ?

sudo pear install PEAR_PackageFileManager_Cli-alpha
pfm /path/to/my/package.xml

How to add a new file ?

sudo pear channel-discover pear.pirum-project.org
sudo pear install pirum/Pirum
git checkout gh-pages
pirum add /path/to/pear-project /path/to/PEAR-PACKAGE-0.0.0.tgz
git add *
git commit -m "bla bla bla bla"
git push origin gh-pages

Wait a few minutes, time for git-hub to update project pages. Then check:
http://tomslabs.github.com/pear/